    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="col text-center">
            <h4>Useful information about blood donation</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Donating blood not only improves the life of the recipient, but also helps the donor stay healthy.</p>
        
<div class="accordion" id="accordionPanelsStayOpenExample">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#panelsStayOpen-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panelsStayOpen-collapseOne">
                        Conditions that make you eligible to donate blood
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="panelsStayOpen-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse ">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                       <li>You must be at least 17 years old</li> 
                       <li>You must weigh at least 50 kg.</li>
                       <li>The percentage of hemoglobin must be suitable for the donation.</li>
                       <li>Pregnant women are not eligible for donation, wait 6 weeks after delivery.</li>
                       <li>The donor must be free of certain diseases that prevent donation.</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#panelsStayOpen-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panelsStayOpen-collapseTwo">
                        What donor is supposed to do before donating 
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="panelsStayOpen-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <li>Get enough sleep, at least 5 hours.</li>
                        <li>Eat a meal before donating.</li>
                        <li>Bring an ID card.</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#panelsStayOpen-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panelsStayOpen-collapseThree">
                        Contraindications to donation
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="panelsStayOpen-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <li>That the person has not made any donations in the last three months.</li>
                        <li>That the donor has not undergone any surgical intervention recently.</li>
                        <li>The donor suffers from any of the following diseases: Blood pressure, diabetes, malaria at least in the last two years, kidney failure, liver enlargement, chest disease, rheumatic fever, thyroid disease, hereditary bleeding and hemorrhage.</li>
                        <li>Pregnant people are not eligible for donation, wait 6 weeks after delivery.</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#panelsStayOpen-collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panelsStayOpen-collapseFour">
                        How long does the donation process take
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="panelsStayOpen-collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Typically 20 minutes. The period to separate each donation from the other for the same person is 3 months because this is the ideal period for the reproduction of blood cells.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#panelsStayOpen-collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panelsStayOpen-collapseFive">
                        Some recommendation for after the donation process
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="panelsStayOpen-collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                       <li>A 10 min rest.</li>
                       <li>Do not exert yourself excessively within two hours of donation</li>
                       <li>Drink fluids to replenish the body.</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#panelsStayOpen-collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="panelsStayOpen-collapseSix">
                        Why shoul I be a blood donor?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="panelsStayOpen-collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                       <li>Every three seconds, someone in the world needs a blood transfusion.</li>
                       <li>Your one donation can save 3 people.</li>
                       <li>The blood donation process restores the body's vitality and activity through the renewal of blood cells.</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
     
